cdata.name: Inmusik
cdata.desc: Inmusik is an ecosystem based on a blockchain database that supports the music industry, streaming, and social interaction, with cryptocurrency rewards and a financial framework on which future music industry applications can be built on. The Inmusik network runs on a dual-token system: SOUND is the fundamental token on which the Inmusik is based. It can be bought or sold as well as being used as a form of payment. Due to the high volatility of the speculative market, the SOUND token value will change daily making too unpredictable for artists to receive payments for streams or for curator's payouts. The Inmusik Cash (IC) is a stable currency pegged to the USD created to address this issue on a long-term basis. It is the token paid out to fans as rewards and to artists/labels for streams/rewards.
